This project is developed as a basic front-end UI for the command-line outputs of glxinfo and vulkaninfo. The application helps in viewing/navigating the OpenGL and Vulkan Information in ease over command-line.
Please do note that this project does not use any OpenGL and Vulkan programming lanuages. The entire application works as a wrapper on the glxinfo and vulkaninfo output.

The latest source code of this program can be found at
https://github.com/arunsivaramanneo/GPU-Viewer

This program uses:
    -  python 2.7 or higher
    -  GTK3+ for the graphical user interface
    -  glxinfo and vulkaninfo for fetching the report

